    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207480/extras/662f54f04d9dfd60458bcc480ccc61af.avif?t=1768472900\" width=616 height=96 /></span><strong>强壮。多肉。毛里。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让传奇般的巨型海象毛里带你踏上一场与众不同的冒险旅程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与一群色彩缤纷、搞笑的动物角色相遇，探索令人难忘的地点，用独一无二的毛里风格碾压你的敌人！<br>准备好你的鳍脚，磨砺你的长牙，成为海象界让特洛伊海伦夜不能寐的英雄！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207480/extras/73978067f44f72da99c35943eba53e39.poster.avif?t=1768472900\" width=760 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207480/extras/73978067f44f72da99c35943eba53e39.webm?t=1768472900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207480/extras/73978067f44f72da99c35943eba53e39.mp4?t=1768472900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验真正的史诗冒险！踏上一场空前的征程！挑战你的勇气，完成你的宿命，随着海象毛里迎接新的挑战。<br>感受脂肪上的风吹拂，从岛屿穿越到岛屿，为那些仅仅敢用眼神冒犯你的人喷出死亡的嘲讽！<br>你是否具备英雄的核心美德和坚定的意志，点燃未来之路的火焰？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的柏拉图理念可能需要重新调整，因为毛里是你脑海中唯一需要的海象！</p>",
